text: Nicolai Philipsen (14 July 1880 - 3 March 1949) was a Danish gymnast. He competed in the men's team event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1880 births Category:1949 deaths Category:Danish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Denmark Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Copenhagen
